title: Bobby Opens His Birthday Gifts + Luke Combs Stops By

description:
Bobby opens his gifts from the show. Luke Combs stops by and talks about how he wrote “Beautiful Crazy” for his fiancé soon after they met. Also, Amy fell for an April Fool’s Day joke.
